    "calories_coverage_pct": 17.7,
    "protein_coverage_pct": 37.8,
    "vitamin_c_coverage_pct": 193.7,
    "iron_coverage_pct": 146.9,
    "note": "v2 KB-aligned crop mix. Potato-heavy caloric zone drives calorie and iron coverage up significantly vs v1. Greenhouse supplements stored rations. Full caloric self-sufficiency is not the goal -- vitamin C, iron, and fresh food morale are the primary contributions. Vitamin D and B12 require stored supplements."
  },
